PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument of Revocation and Amendment wherein the SHUSWAP BAND (a) revokes a 1973 Surrender for leasing and annexes the land concerned to a 1959 Surrender affecting Shuswap Indian Reserve No. 0 in British Columbia, and (b) makes consequential revisions to the legal description of all the surrendered land and places limits on the duration of any Leases and restrictions on how the land may be used.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument of Revocation and Amendment wherein the SHUSWAP
BAND (a) revokes a 1973 Surrender for leasing and annexes the land
concerned to a 1959 Surrender affecting Shuswap Indian Reserve No. 0 in
British Columbia, and (b) makes consequential revisions to the legal
description of all the surrendered land and places limits on the duration
of any Leases and restrictions on how the land may be used.
